```plantuml
@startuml terrenjpeterson_javawatch

actor User
participant RaspberryPi as RP
participant S3Bucket as S3
participant LambdaCheckImage as LCI
participant Rekognition as Rekog
participant LambdaLabelCheck as LLC
participant AmazonDRS as DRS

User -> RP: Capture Image
RP -> RP: Overlay Timestamp
RP -> S3: Upload Image

activate S3
S3 -> LCI: Trigger Lambda Function
deactivate S3

activate LCI
LCI -> Rekog: Analyze Image for Labels
Rekog -> LCI: Return Labels ("Bean")
deactivate LCI

LCI -> LLC: Confirm "Bean" Label Presence
activate LLC
LLC -> LCI: Confirmation Result
deactivate LLC

alt Bean Level Low
    LCI -> DRS: Place Order
else Bean Level Adequate
    LCI -> User: No Action Needed
end

@enduml
```